    <title>Congressional Pay Reduction Act</title>
    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Congressional Pay Reduction Act</b></p> <p>Amends the Legislative Reorganization Act of 1946 to: (1) eliminate automatic cost of living adjustments for Members of Congress, and (2) reduce Members' annual rate of pay to 95% of the annual rate for the most recent pay period preceding the regularly scheduled federal general election held in November 2016. </p>]]></text>
